       $433000\n\n\n# § 打算如何讓社群參與以及回饋意見？\n\n公測平台也是需要公測的~\n\n# § 請說明專案結束時，會產出的開源軟體套件或開放授權文件（請條列個別元件的輸入輸出或其功能）？\n\n> Aws架構細節\n\n> 網頁整體的設計、源碼\n\n# § 請自行定義計畫的工作里程碑與最後的驗收標準 （若沒有達成這些標準的話，我們會不給你錢喔！)\n\n期中：\n\n> 完成網頁\n> 用戶能申請案件\n> 申請後自動配發獨立VPS + 域名\n> 案主能有頁面檢視主機Log檔\n\n期末：\n\n> 測試給予回饋能看到自己點數累積\n> 點數能換商品\n> A/B Testing wizard 上線\n> 至少有1案件運用本平台公測發佈\n\n# § 未來可能進一步的發展？\n\n- 透過每個用戶上傳的comment，可以了解大家的專業項目，後續或能商業化接測試案件。\n- 期望成為g0v新創科技獎助金的評鑑平台之一 ^_^\n\n# § 本計畫目前是否已有、或正在申請其他的資金來源？若有，請說明申請本獎助的內容與原計畫的差異。\n\n目前沒有。\n\n# § 若有專案介紹的投影片，請提供：\n\n沒有。","link":"","leader":{"_id":"5890956b725c74001e88185a","username":"King Wang","name":"Kingston","picture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-XdUIqdMkCWA/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAAAA/4252rscbv5M/photo.jpg?sz=50","provider":"google","bio":"Skill: C, Python, Html, Javascript\nInterested in cloud service. \nExperienced cloud service architecture. Help a company build their e-paper platform by amazon web service before.","created_at":"2017-01-31T13:47:23.277Z","admin_in":[]},"cover":"/uploads/efec2b910f67b549550b3ac3ee578423.jpg","domain":"2017spring","created_at":"2017-01-31T14:19:24.488Z","updated_at":"2017-02-06T17:15:37.478Z","tags":["公測","debug","平台"],"finalist":false,"awarded":false,"followers":[{"_id":"5890956b725c74001e88185a","username":"King Wang","name":"Kingston","picture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-XdUIqdMkCWA/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAAAA/4252rscbv5M/photo.jpg?sz=50","provider":"google","bio":"Skill: C, Python, Html, Javascript\nInterested in cloud service. \nExperienced cloud service architecture. Help a company build their e-paper platform by amazon web service before.","created_at":"2017-01-31T13:47:23.277Z","admin_in":[]}],"contributors":[{"_id":"5890956b725c74001e88185a","username":"King Wang","name":"Kingston","picture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-XdUIqdMkCWA/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAAAA/4252rscbv5M/photo.jpg?sz=50","provider":"google","bio":"Skill: C, Python, Html, Javascript\nInterested in cloud service. \nExperienced cloud servi