\n在服役的這段期間，我組織團隊，發起【工時透明化運動】，架設網頁讓勞工留下工時資訊，希望能夠促進工作資訊的透明化。此外，也製作勞工權益資訊的懶人包，希望一方面可以增進台灣勞工的權益認知，另一方面吸引使用者上來分享資訊。\n目前即將退伍，希望可以將網站的工作資訊項目擴充(薪資、面試經驗、工作經驗)，並整合各大求職平台的職缺資訊，讓台灣的求職者可以方便地搜尋資訊。此外，希望引入商業模式，讓這個專案可以永續進行。\n\n我在專案中的負責的部分: 專案管理 + 網站前端(不包含介面設計)、後端開發 + 勞動權益資訊整理。\n\n網站: https://worktime.goodjob.life/\n前端repo: https://github.com/goodjoblife/WorkTimeSurvey\n後端repo: https://github.com/goodjoblife/WorkTimeSurvey-backend\n\n【技能】\n網站前端: Vue.js, jQuery\n網站後端: Node.js + Express + MongoDB, php + MySQL\n勞動權益資訊: 主要熟悉勞基法\n其他程式語言: C, Python, Java\n其他專業技能: 自然語言處理、機器學習、社群網路分析 (為研究領域)\n\n詳細個人履歷請見: https://www.cakeresume.com/WeiMing\n個人Github repo: https://github.com/barry800414個人Github repo: \n","created_at":"2017-01-26T06:52:53.367Z","admin_in":[]},{"_id":"5891d16b725c74001e881904","username":"丁少弘","name":"丁少弘","picture":"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/-BMXHSoZSU4s/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAAAs/rdr9nJq5Ga0/photo.jpg?sz=50","provider":"google","created_at":"2017-02-01T12:15:39.120Z","admin_in":[]},{"_id":"586f6914e34a29001e1ae475","username":"ymhuang0808","name":"YMHuang","picture":"https://avatars1.githubusercontent.com/u/2720857?v=4","provider":"github","created_at":"2017-01-06T09:53:24.792Z","admin_in":[]},{"_id":"58941a81725c74001e88199e","username":"larisa H","name":"Rosie Hung","picture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-XdUIqdMkCWA/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAAAA/4252rscbv5M/photo.jpg?sz=50","provider":"google","bio":"","created_at":"2017-02-03T05:52:01.350Z","admin_in":[]},{"_id":"589847788dd562001e185bc8","username":"林姵岑","name":"林姵岑","picture":"https://fb-s-a-a.akamaihd.net/h-ak-xtf1/v/t1.0-1/p50x50/15871628_1284473388242023_7056368162977338790_n.jpg?oh=444c5af7bf845025f4b74e896a36a1ca&oe=5941CB29&__gda__=1494297737_585ff97fcaf2ed13773daeeecff8510a","provider":"facebook","created_at":"2017-02-06T09:52:56.172Z","admin_in":[]},{"_id":"58a343bbd92432001e7b64f1","username":"謝文川","name":"謝文川","picture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-NB1vjCJuZbg/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAAAA/CwyUDS5a7_Y/pho