功能）？\n\t是的，整個網站平台的程式碼，資料庫都可以開放用在其它資訊交換\n# § 請自行定義計畫的工作里程碑與最後的驗收標準 （若沒有達成這些標準的話，我們會不給你錢喔！)\n\t好的，工作里程碑，前1個月網站樣版、功能模組、資料庫設計規劃\n第2個月~2.5個月進行程式開發及網站架設，最後0.5個月進行測試及除錯上線\n# § 未來可能進一步的發展？\n\t除了傢俱也可以運用在其它資源交換上面\n# § 本計畫目前是否已有、或正在申請其他的資金來源？若有，請說明申請本獎助的內容與原計畫的差異。\n\t無\n# § 若有專案介紹的投影片，請提供：\n\t無","link":"","leader":{"_id":"588a1b1c29941d001ebebf2a","username":"Leo Lu","name":"Leo Lu","picture":"https://fb-s-b-a.akamaihd.net/h-ak-xta1/v/t1.0-1/p50x50/12187675_1190173044330828_8196171296501568291_n.jpg?oh=786de4e0fe7f42425e7eab7be8a8c406&oe=591127CE&__gda__=1494176062_8cc3b229e677b975c53bdf3df7d7bd64","provider":"facebook","bio":"有多項專案開發經驗及自行架設購物網站經驗","created_at":"2017-01-26T15:51:56.686Z","admin_in":[]},"cover":"/uploads/adb55d720ff431192fb4d5614acf90a3.png","domain":"2017spring","created_at":"2017-01-26T16:27:50.689Z","updated_at":"2017-01-26T16:30:30.357Z","tags":["二手","傢俱","平台","交換"],"finalist":false,"awarded":false,"followers":[{"_id":"588a1b1c29941d001ebebf2a","username":"Leo Lu","name":"Leo Lu","picture":"https://fb-s-b-a.akamaihd.net/h-ak-xta1/v/t1.0-1/p50x50/12187675_1190173044330828_8196171296501568291_n.jpg?oh=786de4e0fe7f42425e7eab7be8a8c406&oe=591127CE&__gda__=1494176062_8cc3b229e677b975c53bdf3df7d7bd64","provider":"facebook","bio":"有多項專案開發經驗及自行架設購物網站經驗","created_at":"2017-01-26T15:51:56.686Z","admin_in":[]},{"_id":"586734969a859b001ee4e61f","username":"yutin1987","name":"YuTin Liu","picture":"https://avatars3.githubusercontent.com/u/2505934?v=4","provider":"github","bio":"簡歷： https://github.com/yutin1987/yutin1987.github.io","created_at":"2016-12-31T04:31:18.491Z","admin_in":[]},{"_id":"58935c75725c74001e881971","username":"蔣宗恩","name":"蔣宗恩","picture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-XdUIqdMkCWA/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAAAA/4252rscbv5M/photo.jpg?sz=50","provider":"google","created_at":"2017-02-02T16:21:09.891Z","admin_in":[]},{"_id":"58a16777f648d8001ea7a839","username":"駱秀碧","name":"駱秀碧","picture":"https://fb-s-b-a.akamaihd.net/h-ak-xpf1/v/t1.0-1/p50x50/12801452_117