說明申請本獎助的內容與原計畫的差異。\n\n本計劃的相關計畫已經申請Google Data Center Community Grant Program，不過申請部分涵蓋律師、當事人與旁聽者針對法庭與判決提出評分的機制。\n\n# § 若有專案介紹的投影片，請提供：\n\n目前暫無","link":"https://sunshine.jrf.org.tw/","leader":{"_id":"58745e508798fb001e7324f1","username":"林雨蒼","name":"林雨蒼","picture":"https://fb-s-c-a.akamaihd.net/h-ak-xtp1/v/t1.0-1/p50x50/13312632_10209426830644671_369862916892753122_n.jpg?oh=51f80379b3a7531f4b3f4a2f8520cd3f&oe=593EDAB8&__gda__=1497351764_80e642fb21c70d95e37b2b7c5fb396af","provider":"facebook","bio":"自由軟體工作者，公民記者，目前任職於民間司改會。","created_at":"2017-01-10T04:08:48.573Z","admin_in":[]},"cover":"/uploads/b38e849852ba68fa05b87a9861fd4bca.png","domain":"2017spring","created_at":"2017-01-10T08:35:44.212Z","updated_at":"2017-02-10T00:29:10.563Z","tags":["司法","判決","司法院","API","爬蟲"],"finalist":true,"awarded":true,"followers":[{"_id":"58745e508798fb001e7324f1","username":"林雨蒼","name":"林雨蒼","picture":"https://fb-s-c-a.akamaihd.net/h-ak-xtp1/v/t1.0-1/p50x50/13312632_10209426830644671_369862916892753122_n.jpg?oh=51f80379b3a7531f4b3f4a2f8520cd3f&oe=593EDAB8&__gda__=1497351764_80e642fb21c70d95e37b2b7c5fb396af","provider":"facebook","bio":"自由軟體工作者，公民記者，目前任職於民間司改會。","created_at":"2017-01-10T04:08:48.573Z","admin_in":[]},{"_id":"586bb374b46ada001e477f35","username":"ChengHan Wu","name":"ChengHan Wu","picture":"https://fb-s-b-a.akamaihd.net/h-ak-xla1/v/t1.0-1/p50x50/12289462_10205371524355271_6891418906384948597_n.jpg?oh=4b31cff5e4080623719a1b07609f20a5&oe=59057AAE&__gda__=1493603912_b80534d0f6b010d2357e7275484f0b67","provider":"facebook","bio":"國立臺北科技大學 資訊工程所 二年級。\n致力於開源專案與社群，希望建立能永續經營的開源商業模式。\n我寫的不是程式，我寫的是理想。","created_at":"2017-01-03T14:21:40.151Z","admin_in":[]},{"_id":"58672bc19a859b001ee4e61c","username":"hsin421","name":"Hsin Hsiao","picture":"https://avatars3.githubusercontent.com/u/7806299?v=4","provider":"github","bio":" 紐約客 - 物理研究生 - 軟體工程師 - 創業人 - 投資人 - g0v 紐約區沒有人 - 紐約哲五志工 - 鍵盤人權鬥士 - 一個孩子的爸","created_at":"2016-12-31T03:53:37.067Z","admin_in":[]},{"_id":"586734969a859b001ee4e61f","