 建立收納功能\n - 六個月\n   - 建立組織功能\n     - 可以建立屬於組織的筆記\n     - 可以設定組織的管理權限\n   - 提供 g0v 專屬組織\n\n# § 未來可能進一步的發展？\n提供商業組織使用、代管私有服務\n\n# § 本計畫目前是否已有、或正在申請其他的資金來源？若有，請說明申請本獎助的內容與原計畫的差異。\n無\n\n# § 若有專案介紹的投影片，請提供：\nhttps://hackmd.io/p/Bk9X2eJT","link":"https://hackmd.io","leader":{"_id":"586bb374b46ada001e477f35","username":"ChengHan Wu","name":"ChengHan Wu","picture":"https://fb-s-b-a.akamaihd.net/h-ak-xla1/v/t1.0-1/p50x50/12289462_10205371524355271_6891418906384948597_n.jpg?oh=4b31cff5e4080623719a1b07609f20a5&oe=59057AAE&__gda__=1493603912_b80534d0f6b010d2357e7275484f0b67","provider":"facebook","bio":"國立臺北科技大學 資訊工程所 二年級。\n致力於開源專案與社群，希望建立能永續經營的開源商業模式。\n我寫的不是程式，我寫的是理想。","created_at":"2017-01-03T14:21:40.151Z","admin_in":[]},"cover":"/uploads/1b1263ce943bfd06a802564bbe738118.png","domain":"2017spring","created_at":"2017-01-07T11:21:11.596Z","updated_at":"2017-02-06T11:49:13.148Z","tags":["Collaborative","Markdown","note"],"finalist":false,"awarded":false,"followers":[{"_id":"5865f94d87e3dc001e549010","username":"ipaaa","name":"ipa ","picture":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/2939042?v=3","provider":"github","bio":"g0v 社群共同發起人，g0v 揪松團坑主，兩個月舉辦一次大松。\n文字、紀錄片、兩個孩子的媽。\n\nhttps://medium.com/@ipaway\nhttp://ipaway.org","created_at":"2016-12-30T06:06:05.327Z","admin_in":[]},{"_id":"586e429c6901c8001e1c6a0d","username":"kjohn01","name":"KJohn","picture":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/8452056?v=3","provider":"github","bio":"Hello world!","created_at":"2017-01-05T12:57:00.988Z","admin_in":[]},{"_id":"586a7ad1a327a4001ee49125","username":"poga","name":"Poga Po","picture":"https://avatars0.githubusercontent.com/u/8631?v=4","provider":"github","bio":"* self-taught programmer.\n* participate g0v.tw since 2013.\n* focus on the back-end, scalability, and decentralization.\n* open source developer. [beaker browser](https://beakerbrowser.com/docs/team.html) contributor.\n\nhttps://www.linkedin.com/in/pogapo","created_at":"2017-01-02T16:07:45.796Z","admin_in":[]},{"_id":"586734969a